<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/22004.Charles_C_Mann"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1217519580p3/22004.jpg);'></div>
